If He’s awakened within us, all our sins
can be washed out because

00:39:50.060 --> 00:39:53.770
He is sakshat Parabrahma, He is sakshat Shri
Ganesh – purity Himself.

00:39:53.770 --> 00:39:59.510
If He’s awakened within us, all our sins
He can, suck in.

