Nonsense! It’s a very subtle action of negative
forces – all anti-God.

00:40:16.160 --> 00:40:22.480
It has nothing to do with God.

00:40:22.480 --> 00:40:26.980
Christ is a part and parcel of God as Shri
Ganesha is.

00:40:26.980 --> 00:40:29.140
There’s no difference between the two.

00:40:29.140 --> 00:40:31.940
He incarnated on this Earth for this particular
purpose.

00:40:31.940 --> 00:40:38.030
Every time you see this church service, “God
came on this Earth, to die for our sins."

00:40:38.030 --> 00:40:43.440
